{"tid":173561,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"互相幫手，搵下童年回憶","createTime":"2017-03-26T09:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T08:25:27.000Z","uid":15639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"880a4e486eb6030ee47f846ecdeadf3763a4b81a","tid":173561,"uid":15639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T09:19:58.000Z","msg":"大家有無試過，突然諗返啲童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜鳩都好，但硬係諗唔返個名，只記得特徵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想開返個post<br />\n大家放底自己搵唔到既童年回憶<br />\n又幫下其他巴絲搵下童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拋個磚，我細個幼稚園食過一隻硬糖<br />\n糖既形狀係車黎既，好想搵返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f8fc8b63b705c3a30663c2d7eda611dd683797","tid":173561,"uid":15639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T09:23:48.000Z","msg":"仲有一套外國卡通<br />\n好似係一家人去啲叢林探險<br />\n會揸埋架巴士去，細個覺得架巴士好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55ccc159451a18a77d69fd0e5f8f1869d7d08e2","tid":173561,"uid":15639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T09:26:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家有無試過，突然諗返啲童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜鳩都好，但硬係諗唔返個名，只記得特徵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想開返個post<br />\n大家放底自己搵唔到既童年回憶<br />\n又幫下其他巴絲搵下童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拋個磚，我細個幼稚園食過一隻硬糖<br />\n糖既形狀係車黎既，好想搵返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲記得係獨立一粒粒包裝<br />\n有啲位透明，見到粒車形既糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6571bcff8d391c1eafb3f94aab4e8e0299fd1a","tid":173561,"uid":15639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T09:28:10.000Z","msg":"無人有遺忘既童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25fb6caffbca94bd1ba86850dabfdb3d7f6a0b91","tid":173561,"uid":71600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T09:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有一套外國卡通<br />\n好似係一家人去啲叢林探險<br />\n會揸埋架巴士去，細個覺得架巴士好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThe Magic School Bus<br />\n鬼馬黃巴士?"},{"pid":"8a69034d043886df1ca44959740a6c109f5057c0","tid":173561,"uid":15639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T09:47:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有一套外國卡通<br />\n好似係一家人去啲叢林探險<br />\n會揸埋架巴士去，細個覺得架巴士好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThe Magic School Bus<br />\n鬼馬黃巴士?</blockquote><br />\n唔係，架巴士 雙層巴黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 巴打你呢套都好似有啲印象"},{"pid":"d7c374d2be81fc393750d2959dfb84fe11cacf0a","tid":173561,"uid":15639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T10:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936da0d85bba801cd0a5608e5f9846ce4618aad1","tid":173561,"uid":15639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T10:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13a657ade9f2ea8b79e88a7d1bab1a00f2dd7df","tid":173561,"uid":15639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30a9dfce9534ea83a61c99680e80740f5f974a5","tid":173561,"uid":15639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8627bd7a11d8c18ec40589102f3d7f9d5759d4","tid":173561,"uid":15639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T01:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\"